# Modelfile for the Gemma 4 e4b Elevator Dispatcher
# Reference: docs/training-plan.md Stage 5
#
# ⚠️ UNVERIFIED — do NOT `ollama create` from this before Stage-4 verification.
# Lane-A audit (2026-06-13): the base `gemma4:e4b` template is `{{ .Prompt }}`
# (`ollama show gemma4:e4b --template`), so the custom TEMPLATE below imposes a
# DIFFERENT render than the G5-validated inference used. It was hand-written in
# Gemma-2 style and is NOT verified against gemma4's official chat_template or the
# LoRA trainer's. Before any GPU run, confirm this TEMPLATE renders the anchor
# messages byte-identically to the trainer's apply_chat_template for the EXACT
# gemma4 base (the render-identity gate, training-plan Stage 5).

FROM gemma4:e4b

# System parameters for deterministic structural mode selection
PARAMETER temperature 0.0
PARAMETER top_p 0.0
PARAMETER num_ctx 4096
PARAMETER stop "<end_of_turn>"
PARAMETER stop "<eos>"

# Official Gemma chat template template syntax matching the HF tokenizer format
TEMPLATE """{{ if .System }}<start_of_turn>user
{{ .System }}

{{ .Prompt }}<end_of_turn>
{{ else }}<start_of_turn>user
{{ .Prompt }}<end_of_turn>
{{ end }}<start_of_turn>model
{{ .Response }}<end_of_turn>
"""
